{"tid":1358782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱凱廸回應何君堯「生路」、「不生路」言論","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:56:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:00:52.000Z","uid":39521,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f83e419f3fe5cbe9e1160bbb7f1f1a6745e61c76","tid":1358782,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯已故父母位於屯門墳墓遭人破壞，何君堯今（24日）凌晨在facebook直播，聲稱是民主派議員朱凱廸的追隨者所為，朱凱廸包庇破壞者，要求他提供線索予警方；指前面有「生路」及「不生路」，要朱凱廸選擇。朱凱廸今早就事件接受《明報》網站查詢及回應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：是否認同何君堯在facebook直播的指控？</strong><br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸：破壞事件並非在眾目睽睽下發生，亦沒有人出來承認責任，根本無法判斷是何人所為。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯過去不斷作出關於我的失實指控，今次亦不例外，這些假消息往往成為他誤導及煽動群眾的工具，做法可恥，形同玩火。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：對何君堯的「生路」、「不生路」言論有何感想？是否感到威脅？</strong><br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸：我認為警方首要調查何君堯在7．21襲擊中的角色。<br />\n<br />\n在目前政治對立嚴重的社會氣氛中，政治人物受襲擊的風險確實提高了。何君堯的威嚇言論是火上加油，我要求他收回言論，不要再煽動暴力，誤導公眾。我未有計劃到警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問：對何君堯已故父母墳墓遭破壞有何回應？</strong><br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸：我反對所有針對政治人物的暴力襲擊，無論其政治立場為何。這個觀點我在昨日的港台訪問中已經提出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190724/s00001/1563937617320/%e3%80%90%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e8%a5%b2%e6%93%8a%e3%80%91%e4%bd%95%e5%90%9b%e5%a0%af%e4%bf%83%e9%81%b8%e3%80%8c%e7%94%9f%e8%b7%af%e3%80%8d%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%8d%e7%94%9f%e8%b7%af%e3%80%8d-%e6%9c%b1%e5%87%b1%e5%bb%b8%e8%a6%81%e6%b1%82%e6%92%a4%e8%a8%80%e8%ab%96%e5%8b%bf%e7%85%bd%e5%8b%95%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190724%2Fs00001%2F1563937617320%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e6%2593%258a%25e3%2580%2591%25e4%25bd%2595%25e5%2590%259b%25e5%25a0%25af%25e4%25bf%2583%25e9%2581%25b8%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25b7%25af%25e3%2580%258d%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25b7%25af%25e3%2580%258d-%25e6%259c%25b1%25e5%2587%25b1%25e5%25bb%25b8%25e8%25a6%2581%25e6%25b1%2582%25e6%2592%25a4%25e8%25a8%2580%25e8%25ab%2596%25e5%258b%25bf%25e7%2585%25bd%25e5%258b%2595%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1Q9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=5ea295a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190724%2Fs00001%2F1563937617320%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e6%2593%258a%25e3%2580%2591%25e4%25bd%2595%25e5%2590%259b%25e5%25a0%25af%25e4%25bf%2583%25e9%2581%25b8%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25b7%25af%25e3%2580%258d%25e3%2580%258c%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25b7%25af%25e3%2580%258d-%25e6%259c%25b1%25e5%2587%25b1%25e5%25bb%25b8%25e8%25a6%2581%25e6%25b1%2582%25e6%2592%25a4%25e8%25a8%2580%25e8%25ab%2596%25e5%258b%25bf%25e7%2585%25bd%25e5%258b%2595%25e6%259a%25b4%25e5%258a%259b&h=3707110e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190724/s00001/1563937617320/%e3%80%90%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e8%a5%b2%e6%93%8a%e3%80%91%e4%bd%95%e5%90%9b%e5%a0%af%e4%bf%83%e9%81%b8%e3%80%8c%e7%94%9f%e8%b7%af%e3%80%8d%e3%80%8c%e4%b8%8d%e7%94%9f%e8%b7%af%e3%80%8d-%e6%9c%b1%e5%87%b1%e5%bb%b8%e8%a6%81%e6%b1%82%e6%92%a4%e8%a8%80%e8%ab%96%e5%8b%bf%e7%85%bd%e5%8b%95%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b</a>"},{"pid":"4fb4bcb1171462348030f7225ce22f3475407d4d","tid":1358782,"uid":270449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"告鳩條弱智仔啦 咁樣恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}